Help, Troubleshooting, General info:
************************************
* (The keygen) will probably not work on virtual machines!

* You may need to run the keygen using an Administrator account
  (right-click on the keygen and choose 'Run as Administrator').

* If the keygen is detected/blocked by your antivirus software then 
  add it to the exclusions lists of real-time protection and auto-scan. 
  You may need to temporarily disable real-time protection and auto-scan 
  when adding the keygen to the exclusions lists, or when using the keygen.

* If the keygen is removed by your antivirus software then restore and exclude it 
  through your antivirus software (Quarantaine or History, or something similar). 

* When succesfully having registered MBAM then backup the keygen and delete it, 
  or exclude it in MBAM, otherwise MBAM may or will detect the keygen.

* MBAM now detects some keygens as "don't.steal.our.software" :p
